Measure type: [481] Declaration of subheading submitted to restrictions (import)
Conditions:
TM609: (Taric Measure) Declarations are allowed on this code only if the following condition is fulfilled: wines of fresh grapes produced in the European Union. Otherwise, another code must be declared.  
(Annex I to Council Regulation (EEC) No 2658/87 on the tariff and statistical nomenclature and on the Common Customs Tariff)
